snippet.textDisplay: Colin,  could you make a single cylinder espresso machine?   just thinking that it would be possible to build an espresso machine wrapped around a small 50cc engine from a bike..   use the water cooling for heating the water, and the transmission output to drive the 9 bar rotary water pump..   you could use an old machine to gather most of the parts you need along with an engine..    a 50cc single cylinder 5-speed espresso machine..   what's not to love about that?
